&lt;li&gt;Own and uphold how design and research work at Stack Overflow include the process, tooling, standards, and craft.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the user experience perspective on how technologists discover and interact with knowledge, and make the ux calls that shape where the product goes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain the highest standards of design craft and research quality across every product surface.&lt;/li&gt;
